      "title": "[正面] Finished Chapter one and I gotta say, despite the ...",
      "summary": "Finished Chapter one and I gotta say, despite the translation being GPT translated, Morimens' story intrigues me throughout the story.\n\nGameplay feels like Limbus Company and the Ui resembles Genshin Impact. Not saying it's bad but just for thought.\n\nThe 4 unique \"playstyles\" as I would say can differentiate most of the gameplay but you'll have to use a specific one later in the game.\n\nGacha wise I haven't had any problems with it maybe due to my barely existent luck in the game but it'll do the job.\n\nDo I recommend playing it? Yeah sure you can try it and if it's not your taste, that's on you. I'll have to play the later chapters to truly experience if it's good or not. 7/10.",
